quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,23,"Hino e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe hunnu…ďe ko …ďe ahodi e Alla kon : hino e ma…ď…ďe timmin…óo takke mun …óen (haa o sahodinaa), hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi ka…ď…ďitii…óo; …ďe wa…ótitaali (ahadi ndin) mbattiigu."
  33,24,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďir hunnu…ďe …ďen sabu gooŇč…óue ma…ď…ďe, O lepta naafiqii…ďe …ďen, si mo yi…ói, maa o ja…ďana …ďe tuubuubuyee. Tawde pellet, Alla laatike kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo ."
  33,25,"Alla ruttidii yeddu…ďe …ďen e tikkere ma…ď…ďe nden, …ďe ke…ďaani mo∆ī∆īere. Alla yonii gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen e hare. Alla siforii Cemmbe e Poolal."
  33,26,"O jipiini …ďen wallindirnoo…ďe jeyaa…ďe e yim…ďe defte …ďen, ka tataaji ma…ď…ďe …óin, O weddii …óen∆īere e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe; fedde goo (e ma…ď…ďe) ho…óon mbara, ho…óon daha kadi fede goo."
  33,27,"O ronini on leydi ma…ď…ďe, e galleeji ma…ď…ďe, e jaw…óe ma…ď…ďe, e leydi ndi on tippaano e mum. Alla siforiikhattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  33,28,"Eey ma yo Annabiijo ! Maakan suddii…ďe maa …ďen: "Si wonii ko nguurndam aduna paala…óon e cu…óaari majjam, haray ngaree mi dakmita on, mi seera on [on tuma] ceergal mo∆ī∆īal."
  33,29,"Si tawii non ko Alla paala…óon, e Nulaa…óo makko on, e galle La'akara …óen, haray pellet, Alla maranii mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďen e moo…óon, njo…ďdi mawndi"."
  33,30,"Eey mon yo suddii…ďe Annabiijo on ! Kala gaddu…óo e moo…óon bone …ďanngu…óo, lepte …óen cowirante mo cowalle …ói…ói! ∆äuum wonii ko newanii Alla."